data.description: Welcome to 117 Reflection Blvd in Auburndale. This captivating property offers a lifestyle of serenity and convenience. With 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, oversized 2 car garage, with 2,150 square feet of living space on a spacious 0.54-acre lot, this home has something for everyone. Enter a world of elegance and charm as you step into this open floor plan residence, where high ceilings, built-in bookcase and other beautifully detailed features that create a sense of grandeur. The beautiful landscaping, complete with fruit trees, mature oak, and crepe myrtle trees, surrounds the home, making it an oasis of natural beauty. Enjoy the fully fenced backyard perfect for your pets, complete with raised garden beds and the garden has been deemed a certified butterfly garden by, creating a tranquil and private outdoor space for your family to enjoy. Located in the gated community of Reflections of Juliana, this neighborhood offers the peace and tranquility you've been searching for. With a low annual HOA fee, quiet streets, and minimal traffic, it's a haven for those seeking a calm and secure environment. Just minutes away from I-4, this location provides easy access to downtown amenities and attractions, making it the ideal hub for work and play. Say goodbye to costly yard maintenance with an irrigation well that will significantly reduce your water expenses. The property boasts a newer water heater, fresh paint, and LVP flooring, ensuring a modern and well-maintained living space. Whether you're a commuter, retiree, or part of a growing family, this home and location are perfect for your lifestyle. Your daily routines will become effortlessly streamlined in this haven of convenience and comfort. Information provided has been deemed reliable but should be verified by buyer(s) and sales associates.
